---
title: Cheesy Mexican Beef and Rice Skillet with Hot Sauce Crema
description: Wanted: A fresh, hearty one-pan meal with enough flavor to stand up to the coldest of winter days. Found: A skillet full of aromatic rice, zesty seasoned beef, and sautéed pepper and onion, topped with gooey melted cheese and hot sauce crema. Reward: bite after bite of deliciousness.
